# Clean Code Principles

Defer to **`rules-typescript-language.mdc`**, **`rules-typescript-validation-and-typeguards.mdc`**, **`rules-bundle-core.mdc`**, **`rules-state-zustand.mdc`**, and **`rules-performance-architecture.mdc`**.

